--------------------------
--- BASIC INSTRUCTIONS ---
--------------------------

  Move desired script to var/www/polyglot/polyglot/scripts 
 
  set read/run permissions for the script


--------------------------------
--- Avconv_convert.sh Config ---
--------------------------------

  > sudo apt-get install libav-tools


--------------------------------
--- brlcad_convert.sh Config ---
--------------------------------

  download and install brl-cad from "http://brlcad.org/"



------------------------------
--- FLAC_convert.sh Config ---
------------------------------

  > sudo apt-get install flac



---------------------------------
--- FreeCAD_convert.sh Config ---
---------------------------------

  > sudo mkdir /var/www/.FreeCAD

  > sudo chown www-data:www-data /var/www/.FreeCAD

  > sudo apt-get install libav-tools




---------------------------------
--- Htmldoc_convert.sh Config ---
---------------------------------

  > sudo apt-get install Htmldoc



--------------------------------
--- ImgMgk_convert.sh Config ---
--------------------------------

  > sudo apt-get install ImageMagick


-------------------------------------
--- LibreOffice_convert.sh Config ---
-------------------------------------
 
  > sudo apt-get install libreoffice

  > sudo mkdir /var/www/.config

  > sudo chown www-data:www-data /var/www/.config
----------------------------------
--- Pdf2djvu_convert.sh Config ---
----------------------------------

  > sudo apt-get install pdf2djvu


-----------------------------------------
--- VCLAudio converter scripts config ---
-----------------------------------------

  > sudo apt-get install vlc-nox












